<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>La Barbería del Patrón 4:13</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  :root {
    --gold: #C9A84C;
    --gold-light: #E8C97A;
    --dark: #0A0A0A;
    --dark-2: #111111;
    --dark-3: #1A1A1A;
    --dark-4: #222222;
    --cream: #F5F0E8;
    --gray: #888880;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    background-color: var(--dark);
    color: var(--cream);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 20px 60px;
    background: rgba(10,10,10,0.95);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%),
      var(--dark);
  }

  .hero-bg-text {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(80px, 15vw, 200px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.03);
    letter-spacing: 10px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    user-select: none;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 20px;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease 0.2s forwards;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 88px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.0;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease 0.4s forwards;
  }

  .hero-title .gold { color: var(--gold); }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 20px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease 0.5s forwards;
  }

  .verse-tag {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease 0.6s forwards;
  }

  .hero-divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 0 auto 50px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease 0.7s forwards;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--dark);
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 16px 44px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease 0.8s forwards;
  }

  .hero-cta:hover {
    background: var(--gold-light);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* SCISSOR DIVIDER */
  .divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 0 60px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .divider-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(201,168,76,0.3), transparent);
  }

  .divider-icon {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  /* SECTION BASE */
  section {
    padding: 100px 60px;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about {
    background: var(--dark-2);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .stat-box {
    background: var(--dark-3);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .stat-box:hover { border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.4); }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray);
  }

  /* SERVICES */
  .services {
    background: var(--dark);
  }

  .services-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 70px;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--dark-3);
    padding: 44px 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .service-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 3px;
    height: 0;
    background: var(--gold);
    transition: height 0.4s;
  }

  .service-card:hover { border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.25); }
  .service-card:hover::before { height: 100%; }

  .service-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .service-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .service-price {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .service-price span {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
  }

  /* GALLERY */
  .gallery {
    background: var(--dark-2);
  }

  .gallery-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: 240px 240px;
    gap: 4px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .gallery-item {
    background: var(--dark-4);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .gallery-item.large {
    grid-row: span 2;
  }

  .gallery-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s;
    filter: brightness(0.85) contrast(1.1);
  }

  .gallery-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); filter: brightness(0.7) contrast(1.1); }

  .gallery-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #111111 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .gallery-item:hover .gallery-placeholder {
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.7);
    border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
  }

  .gallery-placeholder .ph-icon { font-size: 32px; }

  /* BOOKING */
  .booking {
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(201,168,76,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
      var(--dark);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .booking p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--gray);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 50px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .booking-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--dark);
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 18px 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

  .btn-outline {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    background: transparent;
    padding: 18px 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--gold); background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05); }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--dark-2);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
    padding: 60px 60px 40px;
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .footer-brand .brand-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .footer-brand .brand-verse {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .footer-brand p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 280px;
  }

  .footer-col h4 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .footer-col ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .footer-col ul li,
  .footer-col ul li a {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 300;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .footer-col ul li a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  .footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
    padding-top: 30px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .footer-bottom p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(136,136,128,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .footer-bottom .verse-footer {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
  }

  /* SOCIAL ICONS */
  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .social-link {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .social-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
  }

  /* SCROLL INDICATOR */
  .scroll-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease 1.2s forwards;
  }

  .scroll-text {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray);
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
    animation: scrollPulse 2s ease infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scrollPulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scaleY(1); opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { transform: scaleY(1.2); opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* TESTIMONIALS */
  .testimonials { background: var(--dark); }
  .testimonials-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 70px; }
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--dark-3);
    padding: 44px 36px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .testimonial-card:hover { border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.25); }
  .testimonial-quote-mark {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 80px;
    line-height: 0.6;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: block;
  }
  .testimonial-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.75);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .testimonial-stars {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }
  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
    padding-top: 20px;
  }
  .author-avatar {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--dark-4);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .author-info .name {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .author-info .source {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* LOCATION */
  .location { background: var(--dark-2); }
  .location-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .location-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; }
  .location-item { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .location-item-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .location-item-text .label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .location-item-text p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .map-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background: var(--dark-4);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .map-container iframe { width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; filter: grayscale(80%) invert(90%) contrast(90%); opacity: 0.85; }
  .map-overlay-label {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 16px;
    left: 16px;
    background: rgba(10,10,10,0.9);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    section { padding: 70px 24px; }
    .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .location-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 50px; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); grid-template-rows: auto; }
    .gallery-item.large { grid-row: span 1; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    footer { padding: 50px 24px 30px; }
    .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
    .divider { padding: 0 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">La Barbería del Patrón</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#nosotros">Nosotros</a></li>
    <li><a href="#servicios">Servicios</a></li>
    <li><a href="#galeria">Galería</a></li>
    <li><a href="#testimonios">Opiniones</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ubicacion">Ubicación</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contacto">Contacto</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" style="padding: 0;">
  <div class="hero-bg-text">PATRÓN</div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Est. Hermosillo, Sonora</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      La Barbería<br>del <span class="gold">Patrón</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">4 : 1 3</p>
    <p class="verse-tag">"Todo lo puedo en Cristo que me fortalece"</p>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <a href="#servicios" class="hero-cta">Ver Servicios</a>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-indicator">
    <span class="scroll-text">Scroll</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about" id="nosotros">
  <div class="about-text">
    <p class="section-label">Nuestra Historia</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Más que un corte,<br>una experiencia</h2>
    <p>En La Barbería del Patrón 4:13, cada cliente es tratado con el cuidado y la dedicación que merece. No somos solo una barbería — somos un espacio donde el estilo, la tradición y el respeto se encuentran.</p>
    <p>Nuestros barberos están capacitados en las técnicas más actuales sin olvidar los cortes clásicos que nunca pasan de moda. Ven y descubre por qué nos llaman el patrón del estilo en Hermosillo.</p>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61585513437995" class="social-link" target="_blank">FB</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/barberiadelpatron.413" class="social-link" target="_blank">IG</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-stats">
    <div class="stat-box">
      <span class="stat-number">4:13</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Nuestra Fe</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Dedicación</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <span class="stat-number">✂</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Precisión</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <span class="stat-number">★★★★★</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Calidad</span>
    </div>
  </div>
